# ─── Asetek SimSports (0x2433) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Invicta, Forte, La Prima wheelbases, Tony Kanaan Edition
# IMPORTANT: These devices require HID_QUIRK_ALWAYS_POLL on Linux or they will
# infinitely reboot. The modprobe.d conf at
#   packaging/linux/90-racing-wheel-quirks.conf
# sets the required usbhid.quirks kernel parameter automatically.
